Text: I cant get this program work properly.

Works perfectly!
I even updated to version 3.2 (2012-04-24)

=>Install the software (DO NOT START, uncheck the box at the end of installation)
=>Copy Keygen/Patch in the installation folder (C:Program Files (x86)Essential Data ToolsDuplicate File Remover)
=> Run Keygen
=>Click Keygen 
=>Click Patch
=>Run software
=>Click "Enter Key"
=>Click "Offline activation"
=> Copy ALL the key from Keygen
=> Enjoy!
